# Parity item #2: NO pending-saves.txt -> the row must not be drawn. The stub's exact-line
# validation proves absence: picking the row text exits 43 (SELECTION NOT IN LIST) and the
# menu degrades to the honest one-shot Sync now.
desc Pending saves row absent when nothing is pending
config paired
seeded
pick 0|Pending saves (1) - upload now
engine 0|RESULT ok
expect_exit 0
expect_trace SELECTION NOT IN LIST: 'Pending saves (1) - upload now'
